<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0">
    <div
      style="
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      "
    >
      <header style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721772208/assets/logo/Layer_1.png"
          alt="BlackDiamond"
          style="max-width: 150px"
        />
      </header>

      <!-- section -->
      <div
        style="
          background-color: #fff;
          padding: 5px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        "
      >
        <div style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px">
          <img
            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721816601/assets/bannerWelcom/banner.png"
            alt="Welcome Banner"
            style="width: 100%"
          />
        </div>

        <h1
          style="
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
          "
        >
          Welcome Onboard
        </h1>

        <p>Hello <%= data.firstName %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing BlackDiamond.</p>

        <div>
          <p>
            Congratulations, you are step closer to gaining control of your
            finance. BlackDiamond was created with one mission - to make financial
            services accessible and efficient for young Nigerians.
          </p>
          First, upgrade your account in two easy steps so as to enjoy the
          endless possibilities BlackDiamond offers:
          <ul>
            ‚óè Setup your PIN.
          </ul>

          <ul>
            ‚óè Complete your KYC verification by: ‚óã Verifying your BVN
          </ul>

          <ul>
            ‚óè Verify your identity using one of the following NIN, Voters Card,
            Driver's License or Passport.
          </ul>
          You will get an email confirmation on successful verification.
          <p></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          Yaay! Proceed to fund your account, either with your debit card, or
          transfer from a 3rd party bank.
        </p>

        <p>
          Once you are done, you are ready to explore BlackDiamond to see all the
          Crypto services made for you.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing BlackDiamond.</p>
        <p>Regards,</p>

        <p>Tina from BlackDiamond ü•∞.</p>

        <footer
          style="
            background-color: #315b12;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 5px;
            border-radius: 8px;
          "
        >
          <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com"
              style="margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721772838/assets/linkeldn/Vector.png"
                alt="LinkedIn"
                style="width: 24px; height: 24px"
              />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.facebook.com"
              style="margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721772946/assets/facebook/Vector.png"
                alt="Facebook"
                style="width: 24px; height: 24px"
              />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.instagram.com"
              style="margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721772881/assets/instagram/Vector%20%281%29.png"
                alt="Instagram"
                style="width: 24px; height: 24px"
              />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.twitter.com"
              style="margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721772987/assets/twitter/Subtract.png"
                alt="Twitter"
                style="width: 24px; height: 24px"
              />
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <p style="margin: 5px 0; text-align: center">
            Email: <span style="font-weight: bold">support@BlackDiamond.com</span>
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 5px 0; text-align: center">
            Website: <span style="font-weight: bold">www.BlackDiamond.com</span>
          </p>

          <div>
            <a
              href="https://play.google.com"
              style="margin: 0 5px; text-decoration: none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721773096/assets/googleplay/google%20play.png"
                alt="Google Play"
                style="width: 100px"
              />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.apple.com/app-store/"
              style="margin: 0 5px; text-decoration: none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://res.cloudinary.com/do8zvgqpg/raw/upload/v1721773048/assets/appstore/app%20store.png"
                alt="App Store"
                style="width: 100px"
              />
            </a>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
